# Goal Description

Establish a research-grade baseline model for breast cancer histopathology classification using EfficientNet-B3 on the BreakHis dataset. This covers both a binary classification task (Benign vs Malignant) and a 3-class targeted task (IDC, ILC, Fibroadenoma). The implementation will use PyTorch, mixed precision training, robust augmentations, metrics tracking, and visualizations suitable for research presentations.

